Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H3638BA&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpses Call from the Haunted House!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a house! See? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Good evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind if we came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is silly, let's just go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Anybody home?\N-They must be away...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this place...\NLet's go back, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome... I am the\Nkeeper of this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The ghost monster... Occultos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghost monster Occultos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of GOD's Ghost Plan is to\Nfoment chaos by terrifying the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the operation at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the couple who went missing\Nin this forest were young, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Fog...\N-Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he get to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-He must've got lost in the fog!\N-It's really heavy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, stick with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok!\N-Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a house here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's take a look.\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew there was such a\Nbig house in this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they know something\Nabout the missing couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. Try knocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right.\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, what a dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's abandoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's creepy, either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse us for barging in like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a young man and woman\Ndisappeared in this forest yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for them, but...\NHave you maybe seen them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We... know them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They... are dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? They're dead!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-these two-- The\Nmissing couple-- Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you two!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We... told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We... are dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-They vanished!\N-Vanished!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's there!?\N-Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! But I'm afraid you three\Nwon't be leaving this haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Somebody save us!!\N-Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run for it!\N-It won't open, it won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, this is one\Nof GOD's monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I am the\Nghost monster Occultos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you truly think you're\Nmy equal, Jin Keisuke!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold Occultos' psychic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realise now\Nthat you're outmatched?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to waste my time on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The house is disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This wall's disappearing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeletons!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So this really was them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These bones are what's\Nleft of the missing couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we just saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Their ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it! It's like\Nsomeone put a spell on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Jin Keisuke can't see through\NOccultos' three-dimensional illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok, you two call the police.\N-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, help me gather up these bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting... Maybe I'll\Nloosen Occultos' leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then deliver the\Ncoup de grâce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, will one of you come\Nto the bathroom with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's haunted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie, there's no\Nsuch thing as ghosts! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm still scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok, we'll come with you.\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold my stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-See ya.\N-Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's hanged herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in the world is someone\Nparked here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-th-they're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghosts! Ghosts! Ghosts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Save me!!\N-Your life is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Back again, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you murder\Ninnocent people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Interfere with me a\Nthird time and you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too late to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Open{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghosts were popping\Nup all over last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD are trying to throw\NTokyo into a panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to think of a way to\Ncounter his psychic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And while you're thinking, ghosts\Nare scaring people to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Isn't it that security\Nguard's funeral tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Funeral...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wise Bodhisattva of Freedom and Compassion knows\Nthat the body and the Five Aggregates are but Void...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and thus helps those who suffer. O Sariputra,\NMatter is but Void, and Void is but Matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matter becomes Void, and Void becomes Matter. The Five\NAggregates are but Matter. O Sariputra, all is thus Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is birthless, deathless, tainted, pure,\Never-decreasing and ever-increasing--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just his wife and kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People are afraid to come\Nout in case they see a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm frightened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the ghost monster Occultos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Darned GOD monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, this is the third and\Nfinal time you cross me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You won't get away with killing\Nso many innocent people, Occultos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold Occultos' psychic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's Ridol Stick has reflected Occultos' psychic waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses, I was too late! X Rider... Now\NI want to kill you more than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider has vanquished the\Nhorrible ghost monster Occultos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But Apollo Geist's rage only\Nburns hotter! Don't lose, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(0,10)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's monster Salamandra is turning\Npeople into terrifying serpentine mutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Salamandra, master of poisonous vipers,\Nlures the X Rider into the reptile house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Ghouls!? Mysterious Snake-People Appear!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.55,0:24:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.55,0:24:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider